ZH: 我爷爷是一名外科医生。
EN: My grandfather is a surgeon.

ZH: 她要去做外科手术。
EN: She is going to have surgery in the department of surgery.

ZH: 外科医生需要有很强的耐心和技术。
EN: Surgeons need to have strong patience and skills.

ZH: 我很佩服外科医生的勇气和冷静。
EN: I admire the courage and composure of surgeons.

ZH: 外科手术需要在手术室里进行。
EN: Surgery needs to be performed in the operating room.

ZH: 外科团队做了一个十几个小时的手术。
EN: The surgical team performed a surgery that lasted more than ten hours.

ZH: 我表哥是一名专业的外科医生。
EN: My cousin is a professional surgeon.

ZH: 外科医生经常需要熬夜加班。
EN: Surgeons often need to work late nights.

ZH: 在医院里，外科医生是最繁忙的。
EN: Surgeons are the busiest in the hospital.

ZH: 我希望未来能成为一名外科医生。
EN: I hope to become a surgeon in the future.

ZH: 我的外科手术很成功。
EN: My surgery was very successful.

ZH: 外科手术后，她需要休息好几个星期。
EN: After the surgery, she needs to rest for several weeks.

ZH: 外科医生需要非常专注。
EN: Surgeons need to be very focused.

