EN: Surgeons must be very careful and meticulous.

ZH: 外科医生把手术做得非常成功。
EN: The surgeon performed the surgery very successfully.

ZH: 外科医生的技术非常高超。
EN: Surgeons have very advanced skills.

ZH: 外科团队合作默契。
EN: The surgical team works together seamlessly.

ZH: 外科医生需要具备卓越的解剖知识。
EN: Surgeons need to have excellent knowledge of anatomy.

ZH: 外科手术风险相对较高。
